skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: movie tagline quiz
des: Movie Tagline Quiz is a trivia quiz where Alexa gives a movie tagline and you try to guess the correct movie title. For example, Alexa might ask, "What movie has the tagline: An adventure 65 million years in the making?" and you could guess "Jurassic Park". Alexa will ask 10 questions and then give you a final score out of 10. There are over a hundred movies taglines included in this quiz.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
